{"tid":2496543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共教育部收緊對國際學校規管 部分學校考慮撤華","createTime":"2021-04-20T02:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T03:54:31.000Z","uid":52779,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a079ddbfcef9e2d13541438f3ca5e077682e55","tid":2496543,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFXgsoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFXgsoX.jpg&h=e615dc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共近期收緊針對國際學校的指引，要求雙語私立學校等一旦有招收本地學生，便要遵守國家課程指引，事件引發國際教育機構的憂慮，英國《泰晤士報》報道，有50間由英國教育機構營運、在大陸辦學的國際學校，在教學上日益面對當局種種限制，部分有意撤華，不少學校不願意承認自己在華有學校，以免影響西方家長眼中的口碑。<br />\n<br />\n英國教育機構過去若然想在中國開辦國際學校，只能招收持有外國護照的學生，及後由於外國機構開辦的國際學校越來越多，學校之間的競爭日大，部分學校甚至出現收生不足， 於是學校逐漸放寬門檻，招收沒有外國護照的大陸學生。<br />\n<br />\n這亦成為成為中共介入監管的理由，中共教育部今年3月向包括雙語私立學校在內的學校發出新指引，要求任何學校只有會有本地學生就讀，就要遵守國家課程指引。在國家課程指引下，國際學校不能觸及六四事件等敏感議題，所有學校禁止向15歲或以下的中國學生，教授外國課程或使用外國教科書，只能容許使用「小組作業」等外國教學方法。<br />\n<br />\n著名教育雜誌《Good Schools Guide》主編表示，這些安排相當諷刺，因為相關規定令不少在華辦學的國際學校名存實亡，因為它們招收大量大陸學生，但教的不是英式教育，而是中國的課程，與一般中國學校無異。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，有部分學校甚至不想對外承認自己在中國有開學校，因為是「名譽上的風險」（reputationally risky），加上在中共管治之下，即使是辦營機構，亦控制不到它們在華分校的決策。<br />\n<br />\n有北京教育中介公司表示，現時逾30間外國學校在中國開辧學校，截至2019年，分校數目約47間，去年再有14間開幕。但報道表示，有辦學機構因為擔心規管越收越緊，已經計劃撤出中國，改到越南、埃及等地發展。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，在香港親共派高舉「愛國教育」，這套針對學校的辦學指引會否移植到香港，這亦值得大家繼續留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thetimes/status/1383345514624651264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthetimes%2Fstatus%2F1383345514624651264&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=303ac257\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthetimes%2Fstatus%2F1383345514624651264&h=1dcdce20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thetimes/status/1383345514624651264</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ALewerMBE/status/1383379938233905152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FALewerMBE%2Fstatus%2F1383379938233905152&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=5335b14c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FALewerMBE%2Fstatus%2F1383379938233905152&h=678477c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ALewerMBE/status/1383379938233905152</a><br />\n<br />\n原post: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront%2F653&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=8e600fad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/653</a>"},{"pid":"cd1fcfce72fb7db9c34a7d7777a8730d34bb6135","tid":2496543,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c82cad429a9cc8306ac879eca42d0c33e96e394","tid":2496543,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8219ac214aad2e0d1d35e666c2e70de30590af8e","tid":2496543,"uid":289966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e9ea3b68ad8f7f65053d202f5eeb49810abfe3","tid":2496543,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a524cafc8b439f4575b5f3f94ca1861d361b6ff","tid":2496543,"uid":52779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/co